───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
COMMON WORKS CITED ERRORS
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

========================
ERROR 1: WRONG TITLE FORMAT
========================

✗ DON'T:
**Works Cited** (bold)
Works Cited (underlined)
_Works Cited_ (italicized)
Bibliography
References

✓ DO:
Works Cited (plain text, centered)

---

========================
ERROR 2: SINGLE-SPACING
========================

✗ DON'T:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. "Education Pays..."
Carnevale, Anthony P. "The College Payoff..."
(entries cramped together)

✓ DO:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. "Education Pays..."

Carnevale, Anthony P. "The College Payoff..."

(double-spaced between all entries)

---

========================
ERROR 3: NO HANGING INDENT
========================

✗ DON'T:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. "Education Pays, 2023." U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics, U.S. Department of Labor, Sept. 2023, www.bls.gov/careeroutlook/2023/data-on-display/education-pays.htm. Accessed 28 Dec. 2025.

(All lines start at left margin)

✓ DO:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. "Education Pays, 2023." U.S. Bureau of Labor
        Statistics, U.S. Department of Labor, Sept. 2023, www.bls.gov
        /careeroutlook/2023/data-on-display/education-pays.htm. Accessed
        28 Dec. 2025.

(First line at margin, subsequent lines indented)

---

========================
ERROR 4: WRONG ALPHABETICAL ORDER
========================

✗ DON'T:
Federal Reserve Bank of New York...
Bureau of Labor Statistics...
Carnevale, Anthony P...

✓ DO:
Bureau of Labor Statistics...
Carnevale, Anthony P...
Federal Reserve Bank of New York...

(B comes before C comes before F)

---

========================
ERROR 5: MISSING ACCESS DATE
========================

✗ DON'T:
Carnevale, Anthony P. "The College Payoff." Georgetown University Center on
        Education and the Workforce, Georgetown University, 5 Aug. 2021,
        cew.georgetown.edu/cew-reports/the-college-payoff/.

✓ DO:
Carnevale, Anthony P. "The College Payoff." Georgetown University Center on
        Education and the Workforce, Georgetown University, 5 Aug. 2021,
        cew.georgetown.edu/cew-reports/the-college-payoff/. Accessed 28 Dec.
        2025.

---

========================
ERROR 6: WRONG PUNCTUATION
========================

✗ DON'T:
Carnevale, Anthony P, "The College Payoff". Georgetown University...

Errors:
• Comma after "P" instead of period
• Period outside quotation marks

✓ DO:
Carnevale, Anthony P. "The College Payoff." Georgetown University...

---

========================
ERROR 7: MISSING ENTRIES
========================

✗ DON'T:
• Cite (Bureau of Labor Statistics) in essay but not list on Works Cited
• List a source on Works Cited that you never cited in essay

✓ DO:
• Every in-text citation has a matching Works Cited entry
• Every Works Cited entry has at least one in-text citation

---

========================
ERROR 8: USING ABBREVIATIONS
========================

✗ DON'T:
BLS. "Education Pays, 2023."...

✓ DO:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. "Education Pays, 2023."...

(Full name required in Works Cited even if you abbreviated in essay after first use)

---

========================
ERROR 9: WRONG DATE FORMAT
========================

✗ DON'T:
December 28, 2025 (American format)
28/12/2025 (numeric)
12-28-2025 (numeric with dashes)

✓ DO:
28 Dec. 2025 (day month year, month abbreviated)

---

========================
ERROR 10: ARTICLE TITLE NOT IN QUOTES
========================

✗ DON'T:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. Education Pays, 2023. U.S. Bureau...

✓ DO:
Bureau of Labor Statistics. "Education Pays, 2023." U.S. Bureau...

